702483f-b.title: Brooklyn: 9th Street - 4th Avenue
702483f-b.text:
9th Street, st the N. E. corner of Fourth Avenue, showing the St. Thomas Acuinas Roman Catholic Church. The edifice extends north to 8th Street and shows, at the N. E. corner of the latter, the St. Thomas Aquinas School. View 2 shows the Fourth Avenue side of the church,
viewing south from 8th Street.
July 44, 1930
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
